description.narrative:
IFCs expected development impact from a potential investment in Microvast includes: 

Helping China address climate change challenges by financing a company that manufactures energy and cost efficient battery technology;

The success of this Project is expected to accelerate the development of the electric vehicle industry in China. The Project will also assist the government of China to promote the replacement of buses powered by traditional fuel with hybrid or electric buses, thus decreasing the overall carbon emissions and improving cost efficiency over time;

Replacing thousands of buses running on traditional fuel per year with electric batteries could save up to millions of kilograms of CO2; and

Enabling product transfer to other developing regions, such as Southeast and Central Asia
